<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Project Invitation</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h2>Project Invitation</h2>
    <p>Hello {{inviteeName}},</p>
    <p>{{inviterName}} has invited you to join the project <strong>{{projectName}}</strong> as a <strong>{{role}}</strong>.</p>
    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{acceptUrl}}" style="background-color: #2196F3; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; border-radius: 4px;">
        View Project
      </a>
    </p>
    <p>If you believe you received this email by mistake, please contact <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">support</a>.</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br>Your Project Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>